<p source="SHANGBO.RONGSHIYOUCHENG 5.29.1 (STRIPS 5) MACHENGYUAN 5: 322 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.1">融師有成,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.2">厥狀若猩,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.3">有耳不聞,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.4">有口不鳴.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.5">有目不見,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.6">有足不趨.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.7">名則可畏,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-1a.8">步則可侮</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.RONGSHIYOUCHENG 5.29.2 (STRIPS 5-6) MACHENGYUAN 5: 322, 324 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.1">我曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.2">虘茖乎???【5】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.3">[...] 猷時.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.4">我曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.5">虘喬乎???,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.6">弗飲弗食.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.7">物斯可惑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.8">類獸非鼠(?).</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.9">後[食人+弗]昱.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.10">蔑師</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-2a.11">見凶[离].</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.RONGSHIYOUCHENG 5.29.3 (STRIPS 6-7) MACHENGYUAN 5: 324, 326 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.1">毀折戮残,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.2">唯茲作章.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.3">象彼獸鼠,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.4">有足而【6】梏.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.5">沈挫念惟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-3a.6">發揚索[縢]儥.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.RONGSHIYOUCHENG 5.29.4 (STRIPS 7-8) MACHENGYUAN 5: 326, 327 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.1">昔融之是師,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.2">詽尋夏邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.3">蚩尤作兵 [...]【7】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.4">[...] 聞適昜(揚)[=崇扬].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.5">顔色深晦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.6">而志行顯明.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.7">不及愧忿,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0058_tls_001-4a.8">而正固【8】</seg></p>

